---
title: Chicken & Creamy Bechamel Sauce with Potato Mash
description: Bechamel sauce is a fav on a lasagne, but that might have to move over because this chicken needs room to be sauced and then devoured.
It’s all parts mouth-watering and hearty with a fluffy mashed potato and veggies that are sure to get a dose of the loveable creamy sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-creamy-bechamel-sauce-e3aad290.jpg
